title: Macbook Pro A1990-820-01814 Dead
message:
You assume to have short on all caps around CPU, but you didn't post exact (ohm) value.
CPU core and iGPU have very low values as normal.
However, coffee spilled on the CPU power supplies can mean dead CPU now!
